            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_180gc' title='Col. 180GC &mdash; HL Deb 01 July 2003 vol 650 c180GC' name='column_180gc' href='#column_180gc' rel='bookmark'>180GC</a>
            supposed to be Amendment No. 268A, it is tabled in my name and will not be dealt with until we consider a much later grouping.
          </p>
